enable_server_cert_verification	off	Enable server side certificate verification.
enable_view_dependencies	off	Enable created VIEWs to create dependencies on the referenced objects (such as tables)
enabled_log_types	(empty)	Sets the list of enabled loggers
errors_as_json	off	Output error messages as structured JSON instead of as a raw string
experimental_metadata_reuse	on	EXPERIMENTAL: Re-use row group and table metadata when checkpointing.
